object.customQuery:
SELECT Claimstats_Stg.StatSequence, Claimstats_Stg.PolicyNumber, 
case when len(claimstats_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',claimstats_stg.policyversion)             
when len(claimstats_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',claimstats_stg.policyversion)             
else claimstats_stg.policyversion end as policyversion, Claimstats_Stg.LineCd, Claimstats_Stg.RiskCd, Claimstats_Stg.CoverageCd, 
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimNumber, Claimstats_Stg.LosscauseCd, Claimstats_Stg.PostedRecoveryAmt, Claimstats_Stg.ReserveChangeAmt, 
Claimstats_Stg.PaidAmt, Claimstats_Stg.StateCd, Claimstats_Stg.ReserveCd, Claimstats_Stg.BookDt, Claimstats_Stg.TransactionNumber,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionCd, Claimstats_Stg.AddDt, Claimstats_Stg.EffectiveDt,
Claimstats_Stg.MajorPerilCd, Claimstats_Stg.PolicyRef, Claimstats_Stg.FeatureCd, 
Claimstats_Stg.AnnualStatementLineCd, Claimstats_Stg.StatLineCd, Claimstats_Stg.TransactionCd,
Claimstats_Stg.CatastropheNumber, Claimstats_Stg.ReportDt, 
Claimstats_Stg.RecordOnly, Claimstats_Stg.ReserveTypeCd, Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantCd, 
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionNumber, Claimstats_Stg.AdjusterProviderCd, Claimstats_Stg.ExaminerProviderCd, 
Claimstats_Stg.ClassificationCd, Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantTransactionIdRef, Claimstats_Stg.ClaimStatusCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ClaimRef, Claimstats_Stg.ClaimantStatusCd,
Claimstats_Stg.CheckDt,
Claimstats_Stg.CheckNumber,
Claimstats_Stg.CheckAmt,
Claimstats_Stg.SystemId,
Claimstats_Stg.TaxId,
Claimstats_Stg.FeatureSubCd,
Claimstats_Stg.ReserveStatusCd
FROM
 dbo.Claimstats_Stg

fields.name: LossSalvage
fields.expression:
//IIF(UPPER(ReserveCd)='SALVAGE' AND UPPER(ClaimantTransactionCd)//='RECOVERY POST',PostedRecoveryAmt,v_Zero_dec)

fields.name: v_Indemnity
fields.expression:
IIF (ReserveCd = 'Indemnity' AND (ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Payment' OR 
ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Stop Payment' OR ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Void Payment') , PaidAmt ,null)

fields.name: Indemnity_Tier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,to_integer(v_Indemnity)=0,'$0',
v_Indemnity>= 1 AND v_Indemnity< 5000 ,'$1-$5k',
v_Indemnity>= 5000 AND v_Indemnity< 10000 , '$5k-$10k',
v_Indemnity>= 10000 AND v_Indemnity< 250000 , '$10k-$25k',
v_Indemnity>= 25000 AND v_Indemnity< 50000 , '$25k-$50k',
v_Indemnity>= 50000 AND v_Indemnity< 75000 , '$50k-$75k',
v_Indemnity>= 75000 AND v_Indemnity< 100000 ,'$75k-$100k',
v_Indemnity>= 100000 , '$100k+',null)

object.name: addr
object.customQuery:
select
b.systemid as Systemid,
b.id as Id,
c.Addr1 as Addr1,
c.addr2 as Addr2,
c.City as City,
c.StateProvCd as StateProvCd,
c.PostalCode as PostalCode
from partyinfo a join claimanttransaction b
on a.systemid=b.systemid
and a.parentid=b.id
and a.cmmcontainer='Claim'
and b.cmmcontainer='Claim'
left join addr c
on a.id=c.parentid
and a.systemid=c.systemid
and c.cmmcontainer='Claim'

object.name: claimanttransaction
object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct
	   c.Required1099Ind as Required1099Ind, 
       a.SystemId as SystemId, 
	   a.Id as Id 
  FROM claimanttransaction a left join partyinfo b
    on a.id=b.parentid
   and a.systemid=b.systemid
   and a.cmmcontainer=b.cmmcontainer
  left join taxinfo c
    on b.id=c.parentid
   and c.systemid=b.systemid

fields.name: o_LossCauseCd
fields.expression:
IIF(in(CoverageDesc, 'Home Cyber Protection', 'Cyber Liability Insurance')
, CoverageDesc, 
IIF(CoverageCd='HCPC', 'Home Cyber Protection',   
IIF(CoverageCd='CLI','Cyber Liability Insurance',
LosscauseCd)
)
)
